"\"Single\" displays individual agent nodes. \"Combine\" displays all agents "
"in a single node. \"Hide\" does not display queue agents."
msgstr ""
"\"Single\" toont individuele agentenknooppunten. \"Combineert\" toont alle "
"agents in één knooppunt. \"Verbergen\" toont geen wachtrijen agents."

